pros:
Flexibility - culture of engagement and development of individuals and teams;
Passion - it is a place full of passionate people focused on the task of supplying wholesome water to our customer before treating it and returning it safely to the environment;
Variety - the scope and opportunity of roles within the company are significant, particularly when including the roles within our alliance partners (who range from IT through to facilities management);
Well-being - the business really does care about all employees and has been on a significant journey over the last few years to improve employee support as well as flexibility of benefits/working environment;

1. more knowledge can learn from the company and its suppliers;
2. Good place to develop your capability and career;
3. Well-paid as long as you work hard and effectively;
4.work on the things not on the people;

Good work-life balance;
Greate people;
Great environment;
Fair and well established career plan; 
Great career opportunities;
Good perks (Health care for me and my family, anual bonus, 500 € flex benefits per year, RSUs);
Good bonus policy, including RSUs;

Fantastic management support;
Very competitive package with many add-ons available;
Good development opportunities available worldwide;
Very responsible and respectful when it comes to employees' work/life balance;
